Hi <%= @name %>,

To reset your password with the Engine Yard phone system, click the link below:

<%= reset_password_url(:token => @token) %>

You will be brought to a page which will prompt you to change your password. Please choose something which you can remember!

When you log in, you can do the following:

 - Configure the phone number called for any groups to which you've been assigned.
 - Configure your vacation status.
 - View extensions of other members in the phone system
 - View details about the groups in the phone system

